- Siap.

269
00:20:33,640 --> 00:20:34,520
Siap, Sutradara.

270
00:20:36,400 --> 00:20:37,240
Mulai!

271
00:20:37,880 --> 00:20:39,360
Baik, ayo.

272
00:20:39,360 --> 00:20:40,760
Kameramen, siap.

273
00:20:41,680 --> 00:20:42,720
Ayo, rekam.

274
00:20:43,720 --> 00:20:47,800
Bersiap! Satu, dua, tiga! Lompat!

275
00:20:52,720 --> 00:20:53,560
Cut!

276
00:20:54,000 --> 00:20:54,840
Lewat!

277
00:20:59,620 --> 00:21:01,320
- Tidak apa-apa, Kak?
- Tidak apa-apa.

278
00:21:03,960 --> 00:21:04,800
Tidak apa-apa.

