323
00:24:56,240 --> 00:24:57,080
Lebih keras!

324
00:24:58,040 --> 00:24:59,320
Itu rokokku!

325
00:25:00,200 --> 00:25:01,040
Ketua!

326
00:25:01,720 --> 00:25:04,400
Kakinya sampai tidak tertutup.
