349
00:26:58,800 --> 00:26:59,640
Kenapa?

350
00:27:00,120 --> 00:27:01,640
Aku teringat perkataanmu padaku.

351
00:27:01,960 --> 00:27:04,360
Kau bilang, sekarang bagiku,

352
