bersinar bersama♪

404
00:30:53,700 --> 00:30:58,820
♪Wajah orang pergi ke mana♪

405
00:31:03,260 --> 00:31:08,220
♪Bunga persik masih tersenyum
di musim semi♪

406
00:33:12,240 --> 00:33:15,160
Aku sanggup minum.
Kenapa kau gantikan aku minum?

407
00:33:16,960 --> 00:33:20,240
Demi kau, aku rela.

408
00:33:21,440 --> 00:33:22,920
Bagaimana jalannya?

409
00:33:23,800 --> 00:33:25,080
Belok kiri atau kanan?

410
00:33:26,160 --> 00:33:28,080
- Di sini.
- Di sini?

411
00:33:28,280 --> 00:33:29,120
Di sini?

412
00:33:29,800 --> 00:33:30,640
Di sini.

413
00:33:31,320 --> 00:33:32,160
Sempit sekali.

414
00:33:34,440 --> 00:33:37,240
Kuberi tahu padamu,
kalau bawa orang pulang,

415
00:33:37,240 --> 00:33:38,560
